These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-1::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, canasta
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, soy-milk
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, vegafina, ritmeester
City: miami, hamburg, prague
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, blood-red, fuchsia
House: tower, modern, ranch-style
 1. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 2. the person traveling to miami is not to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##8
 3. the person playing canasta is not to the left of the vegafina-smoker##8
 4. the davidoff-smoker is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 5. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
 6. the modern house is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
 7. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the right of the person who likes fuchsia##5
 8. the modern house is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
10. the modern house is not to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##8
11. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1
12. the person traveling to prague is not to the right of the person drinking mirinda##8
13. the person traveling to prague is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the person playing backgammon##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Game          | backgammon | bridge | canasta    |
| Beverage           | tea | mirinda   | soy-milk     |
| Cigar   | davidoff     | vegafina   | ritmeester       |
| City   | hamburg    | prague   | miami     |
| Color   | fuchsia    | ivory   | blood-red |
| House     | ranch-style     | tower | modern     |

