House: tower, modern, wooden
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, azalea
There 3 different types of food: lemon, apple, pumpkin
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, october, november
 1. the person who growsbellflower is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
 2. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##8
 3. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the fan of reggae##5
 4. the person eating pumpkin is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
 5. the fan of disco is between the person playing backgammon and the person eating apple##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 7. the fan of reggae is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
 8. the wooden house is somewhere between the fan of indie and the person playing backgammon##7
 9. the tower house is not the fan of disco##6
10. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who's birthday is in november##2
11. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the modern house##1
12. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |     3     |
| Music-Genre      | reggae       | disco         | indie      |
| Game         | backgammon     | scrabble         | mah-jongg    |
| House           | tower  | wooden | modern |
| Flower   | bellflower    | balloon-flower        | azalea      |
| Food         | pumpkin  | lemon        | apple    |
| Birthday     | july | october      | november      |

