.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, swimming, rowing
3 different games are played: poker, snooker, backgammon
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, dannemann, swisher
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, scooter, ship
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, october, january
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, purple, brown
 1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the person driving the ship is not the person who likes purple##6
 3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 4. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
 5. the person playing snooker is not the person driving the bus##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the dannemann-smoker##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5
10. the person who likes ivory is the person who's sport is rowing##1
11. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
12. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person who likes purple##8

