 4. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 5. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 8. the person who likes chestnut is between the person drinking water and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 9. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the russian##1
10. the russian is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
11. the person who likes yellow is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
