.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, drawing, chess
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, december, april
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, car, snowmobile
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, brazilian, colombian
3 different games are played: billiard, whist, poker
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, hot-chocolate
 1. the nigerian is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
 2. the person drinking cola is the person driving the car##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8
 4. the person driving the scooter is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 5. the brazilian is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person playing whist##1
 7. the nigerian is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 9. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
10. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
11. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
12. the person driving the car is not to the right of the colombian##8
13. the colombian is the person who's birthday is in december##1
14. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
15. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby          | drawing   | camping     | chess       |
| Birthday           | april | october    | december |
| Transport   | car   | scooter | snowmobile          |
| Nationality   | brazilian     | nigerian   | colombian      |
| Game           | billiard       | whist     | poker        |
| Beverage         | cola   | coffee  | hot-chocolate      |

 